      "para_id": "Q004276.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Idattu , grandchild of Ebarat , child of Kindattu , Utu's shepherd , Inana's beloved , king of Anšan , king of the Šimaškians and Elam , Kiten-rakittapi , the grand vizier of Elam and chancellor , his servant , fashioned this ( bowl ) ."
    }
  ],
